question.query: what have been the top projects to raise over the last 30 days

steps.text:
Here are the biggest crypto / crypto-adjacent raises I can find from the last 30 days (rough window: ~Dec 14, 2025 → Jan 13, 2026). I’ve listed name, amount, round/type, date and a source for each. Want this as a CSV or deeper write-up on any of them?

Top raises (last ~30 days)
1. Rain — $250M (Series C) — Jan 9, 2026  
   Source: PR Newswire / Coinpaper / coverage summary: https://www.prnewswire.com/apac/news-releases/rain-raises-250m-series-c-to-scale-stablecoin-powered-payments-infrastructure-for-global-enterprises-302657107.html

2. HashKey (HashKey Capital) — $250M (first close of Fund IV) — Dec 24, 2025  
   Source: CoinDesk / HashKey announcement: https://www.coindesk.com/business/2025/12/24/hashkey-capital-s-usd500-million-target-blockchain-fund-raises-usd250-million-in-first-round

3. BlackOpal — $200M (anchor facility / RWA tokenization facility) — Jan 8–9, 2026  
   Source: GlobeNewswire / Crypto.news summary: https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/01/08/3215748/0/en/BlackOpal-Secures-200M-to-Tokenize-Brazilian-Credit-Card-Receivables.html

4. RedotPay — ~$107M (Series B) — Dec 16, 2025  
   Source: PR/press coverage (CoinDesk/CoinMarketCap): https://www.coindesk.com/markets/2025/12/16/hong-kongs-redotpay-raises-over-usd100-million-series-b-to-push-stablecoin-payments-globally/

5. Olea — $30M (Series A) — Dec 16, 2025  
   Source: Company release / Olea: https://olea.net/olea-secures-us30-million-series-a-funding-to-accelerate-innovation-in-global-trade-finance/index.html

6. Babylon — $15M (strategic/VC investment — a16z Crypto) — Jan 7, 2026  
   Source: Coverage: https://crypto.news/babylon-15m-investment-a16z-bitcoin-staking-2025/

7. ETHGas — $12M (seed) — Dec 17, 2025  
   Source: CryptoTicker: https://cryptoticker.io/en/ethgas-raises-dollar12m-as-it-launches-ethereums-first-blockspace-futures-market/

8. YO Labs — $10M — Dec 14, 2025  
   Source: CoinDesk: https://www.coindesk.com/web3/2025/12/13/yo-labs-raises-usd10m-to-scale-cross-chain-crypto-yield-optimization-protocol

9. HabitTrade — $10M — early Jan 2026 (listed in VC roundup)  
   Source: Messari / VC weekly roundup mentioning HabitTrade among notable deals

10. ZenChain — $8.5M — early Jan 2026 (mentioned in VC roundup)  
    Source: Messari / VC weekly roundup

Notes / caveats
- I focused on crypto / Web3 / stablecoin / RWA-tokenization deals in the period; some large AI / infra raises (xAI, Anthropic) also closed in the same window but they’re outside pure-crypto scope.  
- Some items (e.g., BlackOpal) were structured facilities / anchor commitments rather than equity VC rounds — I included them because they’re major capital inflows into tokenization / RWA crypto infrastructure.  
- Coverage and reported amounts vary by outlet; if you need fully validated deal terms I can open primary press releases or filings and compile a verified table (amount, type, lead investors, valuation if disclosed).

Would you like:
- a downloadable CSV of these deals,
- a deeper profile on any of the projects (team, token, roadmap, investor list), or
- a filtered list (only token raises / only equity rounds / only on-chain treasury buys)?
